<subSubSection id="9D66E77C7A49794317FF27FAB06B5211" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" type="taxon discussion">
<paragraph id="0A35A2CAE604245DDC3AF4044866EAF9" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">Taxon discussion</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D502B96829995026CF9D0AD55132587D" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">
<taxonomicName id="DE1011CE8AA0DBC2525BBF3362AB6DE7" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Ranunculus" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Ranunculus platanifolius" order="Ranunculales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platanifolius">
<emphasis id="D055C4A11F53FBEBE83A77C66B13064B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">Ranunculus platanifolius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is widespread in Europe, but in Greece, it is restricted to a few mountains in the north (
<bibRefCitation id="309CC9BBAEF973D680486291A4B7EFE7" author="Dimopoulos, P." journalOrPublisher="Botanischer Garten und Botanisches Museum Berlin-Dahlem, Berlin; Hellenic Botanical Society, Athens" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7668013" refString="Dimopoulos, P., Raus, T., Bergmeier, E., Constantinidis, T., Iatrou, G., Kokkini, S., Strid, A., D.Tzanoudakis, , 2013. Vascular plants of Greece: An annotated checklist. Botanischer Garten und Botanisches Museum Berlin-Dahlem, Berlin; Hellenic Botanical Society, Athens" title="Vascular plants of Greece: An annotated checklist" year="2013">Dimopoulos et al. 2013</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="FE730DEF960A6300BCEBDFAA2843C517" author="Strid, A." journalOrPublisher="Society for the Protection of Prespa, Agios Germanos, Prespa" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7669537" refString="Strid, A., Bermeier, E., Fotiadis, G., 2020. Flora and Vegetation of the Prespa National Park, Greece. Society for the Protection of Prespa, Agios Germanos, Prespa" title="Flora and Vegetation of the Prespa National Park, Greece" year="2020">Strid et al. 2020</bibRefCitation>
). In the floristic region of North Pindos, 
<taxonomicName id="9783EE8E191C297B9CF6707C41CBAB1F" genus="R." lsidName="R. platanifolius" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" rank="species" species="platanifolius">
<emphasis id="D675674A9DC9B36B36E94F5D2078708F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">R. platanifolius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been recorded from the mountains of Timfi, Smolikas and Gramos (
<bibRefCitation id="70D26E57AE2F33F616B45F65CE90A9DD" author="Strid, A." journalOrPublisher="Cambridge University Press, Cambridge" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7669378" refString="Strid, A., 1986. Mountain flora of Greece 1. Cambridge University Press, Cambridge" title="Mountain flora of Greece 1" year="1986">Strid 1986</bibRefCitation>
). This locality on Mt. Vasilitsa adds a new mountain massif to the distribution of the species.
</paragraph>
